data.description: OPEN HOUSE Sat 6/19 12 - 2pm - Beautifully and lovingly maintained home on a corner lot (on the corner of Sunnyside Lane and Heritage Drive). INGROUND POOL! Lots of extras, updates and upgrades. New HVAC upstairs, downstairs HVAC 6 years old, new gutters, newer Hardie board siding, new down spouts, gutter-guards, new windows, beautiful kitchen with brand new Frigidaire Professional line of appliances, including convection microwave, security system, new roof, STUNNING SUNROOM overlooking pool.
